manifests.contents:
[workspace]
members = ["backend", "desktop", "frontend", "ml", "ml-cmd"]
resolver = "2"

[workspace.dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.98"
log = "0.4.27"

[workspace.dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.219"
features = ["derive"]

[workspace.dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.42.0"
features = ["full"]

[profile.release]
debug = false
lto = true
codegen-units = 1
panic = "abort"
incremental = false
overflow-checks = false

[profile.release.package]

[profile.dev]
debug = true
overflow-checks = true

[profile.dev.package]

[package]
name = "backend"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.8"
features = ["macros", "json", "multipart"]

[dependencies.log]
workspace = true

[dependencies.serde]
workspace = true

[dependencies.tokio]
workspace = true

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.6.4"
features = ["cors", "trace"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1"
features = ["v4"]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "backend"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "desktop"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "desktop"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "frontend"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0.140"
wasm-bindgen-futures = "0.4.50"

[dependencies.log]
workspace = true

[dependencies.ml]
path = "../ml"

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12.15"
features = ["json"]

[dependencies.web-sys]
version = "0.3"
features = ["HtmlCanvasElement", "WebGl2RenderingContext", "MouseEvent"]

[dependencies.yew]
version = "0.21"
features = ["csr"]

[features]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "frontend"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "ml"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
glam = "0.30.3"
zip = "3.0.0"

[dependencies.burn]
version = "0.17.0"
features = ["wgpu", "autodiff"]

[dependencies.tokio]
workspace = true

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "ml"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["lib"]

[package]
name = "ml-cmd"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies.anyhow]
workspace = true

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.5.38"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.ml]
path = "../ml"

[dependencies.tokio]
workspace = true
features = ["rt", "rt-multi-thread", "macros"]

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "ml-cmd"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
